event.title: Banking Sector Summit 2016
event.description:
Banking Sector Summit 2016

This event discusses the importance of banking sector digitization and information security management. Almost all banks in India were computerized and have their own IFSC and micr codes for online transactions. Here is some sample data of state bank of India kolkata branches.
